name: Pay with PayPal
descriptionHtml:
Test

async () => {
  let blockId;
  await (0, _reporter.testStep)("Add a Pay with PayPal block", async () => {
    await blockEditor.waitForAvailableBlock(_simplePayments.default.name());
    blockId = await blockEditor.insertBlock(
      _simplePayments.default.name(),
      _simplePayments.default.title()
    );
  });
  await (0, _reporter.testStep)(
    "Fill details of Pay with PayPal block",
    async () => {
      const spBlock = new _simplePayments.default(blockId, page);
      await spBlock.fillDetails();
    }
  );
  await (0, _reporter.testStep)(
    "Publish a post and assert that Pay with PayPal block is rendered",
    async () => {
      await blockEditor.selectPostTitle();
      await blockEditor.publishPost();
      await blockEditor.viewPost();
      const frontend = await _postFrontend.default.init(page);

      expect(
        await frontend.isRenderedBlockPresent(_simplePayments.default)
      ).toBeTruthy();
    }
  );
};
